Class CompactVirtualFileSet

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<VirtualFile>, java.util.Collection<VirtualFile>, java.util.Set<VirtualFile>

    public class CompactVirtualFileSet
extends java.util.AbstractSet<VirtualFile>
    Set of VirtualFiles optimized for compact storage of very large number of files Remove operations are not supported. NOT thread-safe.
